$lang['Just like in decimal, after 16 symbols have been used in Hexadecimal, the order of numbers starts over again at zero. So, hexadecimal 10 is equal to decimal 16, and hexadecimal 11 is equal to decimal 17. And so on!'] = 'Eżatt bħal fid-deċimali, wara li ntużaw 16-il simbolu f&#39;Hexadecimal, l-ordni tan-numri terġa&#39; tibda mill-ġdid f&#39;żero. Allura, eżadeċimali 10 huwa ugwali għal deċimali 16, u eżadeċimali 11 huwa ugwali għal deċimali 17. U l-bqija!';
